INSERT INTO necs_goods VALUES('1605','72','0','DT001605','漫步者E10 新款','+','196','19','','998','0.000','0.00','524.00','0.00','0','0','1','漫步者E10 新款 漫步者 E10 电脑音箱','','<p align=\"center\" style=\"widows: 2; text-transform: none; text-indent: 0px; font: 12px/20px Tahoma; white-space: normal; orphans: 2; letter-spacing: 2px; color: rgb(102,102,102); word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-size-adjust: auto; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px\"><b>漫步者e10&mdash;&mdash;时尚蜗牛震撼来袭</b></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify; widows: 2; text-transform: none; text-indent: 0px; font: 12px/20px Tahoma; white-space: normal; orphans: 2; letter-spacing: 2px; color: rgb(102,102,102); word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-size-adjust: auto; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px\">漫步者时尚e系列产品，总是在提供&ldquo;好声音&rdquo;的同时，还能以无限创意的工业设计，为消费者提供&ldquo;赏心悦目&rdquo;的视觉享受。作为漫步者e系列新品，采用卡通蜗牛造型的e10既有着颠覆传统的外观设计，同时其强悍的低音效果与均衡的中高音表现会让你震惊，在它小巧可爱的身体里竟有如此动听的声音。</p>\r\n<p align=\"center\" style=\"widows: 2; text-transform: none; text-indent: 0px; font: 12px/20px Tahoma; white-space: normal; orphans: 2; letter-spacing: 2px; color: rgb(102,102,102); word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-size-adjust: auto; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px\"><img border=\"0\" alt=\"\" width=\"500\" src=\"http://www.edifier.com/sce2009/product/speaker/e10/1.jpg\" /></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify; widows: 2; text-transform: none; text-indent: 0px; font: 12px/20px Tahoma; white-space: normal; orphans: 2; letter-spacing: 2px; color: rgb(102,102,102); word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-size-adjust: auto; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px\"><b>创意蜗牛设计，造型赏心悦目</b></p>\r\n<p align=\"center\" style=\"widows: 2; text-transform: none; text-indent: 0px; font: 12px/20px Tahoma; white-space: normal; orphans: 2; letter-spacing: 2px; color: rgb(102,102,102); word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-size-adjust: auto; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px\"><img border=\"0\" alt=\"\" width=\"500\" src=\"http://www.edifier.com/sce2009/product/speaker/e10/2.jpg\" /></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify; widows: 2; text-transform: none; text-indent: 0px; font: 12px/20px Tahoma; white-space: normal; orphans: 2; letter-spacing: 2px; color: rgb(102,102,102); word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-size-adjust: auto; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px\">要好声音，也要好设计，这是漫步者e系列音箱一贯宗旨。呈现在你面前的漫步者e10，初见，便会轻易被其可爱的&ldquo;蜗牛&rdquo;外形所俘获。在看腻了千篇一律方方正正的音箱箱体之后，一只离经叛道的&ldquo;蜗牛&rdquo;，会让音箱从此变得与众不同。</p>\r\n<p align=\"center\" style=\"widows: 2; text-transform: none; text-indent: 0px; font: 12px/20px Tahoma; white-space: normal; orphans: 2; letter-spacing: 2px; color: rgb(102,102,102); word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-size-adjust: auto; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px\"><img border=\"0\" alt=\"\" width=\"500\" src=\"http://www.edifier.com/sce2009/product/speaker/e10/3.jpg\" /></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify; widows: 2; text-transform: none; text-indent: 0px; font: 12px/20px Tahoma; white-space: normal; orphans: 2; letter-spacing: 2px; color: rgb(102,102,102); word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-size-adjust: auto; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px\">漫步者e10为两件式设计，底座为形似蜗牛壳的低音箱体，中高音独立箱体则为形似蜗牛本体的长条状设计，造型简洁，棱角分明，与底座紧密连接。e10小巧的体积与直线曲线完美结合的新颖外观设计，尤其适合桌面空间有限而又追求个性品味的消费者。</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify; widows: 2; text-transform: none; text-indent: 0px; font: 12px/20px Tahoma; white-space: normal; orphans: 2; letter-spacing: 2px; color: rgb(102,102,102); word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-size-adjust: auto; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px\"><b>双重低音，呈现强悍低频表现</b></p>\r\n<p align=\"center\" style=\"widows: 2; text-transform: none; text-indent: 0px; font: 12px/20px Tahoma; white-space: normal; orphans: 2; letter-spacing: 2px; color: rgb(102,102,102); word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-size-adjust: auto; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px\"><img border=\"0\" alt=\"\" width=\"500\" src=\"http://www.edifier.com/sce2009/product/speaker/e10/4.jpg\" /></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify; widows: 2; text-transform: none; text-indent: 0px; font: 12px/20px Tahoma; white-space: normal; orphans: 2; letter-spacing: 2px; color: rgb(102,102,102); word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-size-adjust: auto; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px\">漫步者e10除了拥有赏心悦目的造型设计之外，更令人惊讶的，还在于它的音质表现。作为漫步者时尚e系列新作，e10采用与e系列高端产品e30一致的2.2声学结构，即在小巧的&ldquo;蜗牛&rdquo;箱体之内，主副箱均包括了低音和中高音发声单元，确保了纯正细腻的音色和震撼澎湃的低频效果。</p>\r\n<p align=\"center\" style=\"widows: 2; text-transform: none; text-indent: 0px; font: 12px/20px Tahoma; white-space: normal; orphans: 2; letter-spacing: 2px; color: rgb(102,102,102); word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-size-adjust: auto; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px\"><img border=\"0\" alt=\"\" width=\"500\" src=\"http://www.edifier.com/sce2009/product/speaker/e10/5.jpg\" /></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify; widows: 2; text-transform: none; text-indent: 0px; font: 12px/20px Tahoma; white-space: normal; orphans: 2; letter-spacing: 2px; color: rgb(102,102,102); word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-size-adjust: auto; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px\">对低音的追求是e10的重中之重。在圆润的低音箱体内，漫步者的设计师分别设置有左右两组独立的重低音系统，均由一只特制的3寸高效能扬声器和特别增加的被动辐射器构成，可轻松提供20W低频输出，以小巧的箱体空间，迸发令人惊异的低音效果。</p>\r\n<p align=\"center\" style=\"widows: 2; text-transform: none; text-indent: 0px; font: 12px/20px Tahoma; white-space: normal; orphans: 2; letter-spacing: 2px; color: rgb(102,102,102); word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-size-adjust: auto; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px\"><img border=\"0\" alt=\"\" width=\"500\" src=\"http://www.edifier.com/sce2009/product/speaker/e10/6.jpg\" /></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify; widows: 2; text-transform: none; text-indent: 0px; font: 12px/20px Tahoma; white-space: normal; orphans: 2; letter-spacing: 2px; color: rgb(102,102,102); word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-size-adjust: auto; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px\">漫步者对于低频的重视还不止于此，在左右两组独立的低音系统基础上，设计师又在中高音独立箱体中增加了一只被动辐射器，这样在每个箱体中均包含三个主动式单体和两个被动幅射器，叠加双重低音效果，能最大限度提升音频性能，提供更加出众的低音表现。</p>\r\n<p align=\"center\" style=\"widows: 2; text-transform: none; text-indent: 0px; font: 12px/20px Tahoma; white-space: normal; orphans: 2; letter-spacing: 2px; color: rgb(102,102,102); word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-size-adjust: auto; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px\"><img border=\"0\" alt=\"\" width=\"500\" src=\"http://www.edifier.com/sce2009/product/speaker/e10/7.jpg\" /></p>\r\n<p align=\"center\" style=\"widows: 2; text-transform: none; text-indent: 0px; font: 12px/20px Tahoma; white-space: normal; orphans: 2; letter-spacing: 2px; color: rgb(102,102,102); word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-size-adjust: auto; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px\"><img border=\"0\" alt=\"\" width=\"500\" src=\"http://www.edifier.com/sce2009/product/speaker/e10/8.jpg\" /></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify; widows: 2; text-transform: none; text-indent: 0px; font: 12px/20px Tahoma; white-space: normal; orphans: 2; letter-spacing: 2px; color: rgb(102,102,102); word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-size-adjust: auto; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px\">而e10的每组中高音系统，则由一对1.5寸扬声器构成，虽然体积小巧，却可以提供高达16W(2*2*4W)的中高音额定功率输出而不失真。</p>\r\n<p align=\"center\" style=\"widows: 2; text-transform: none; text-indent: 0px; font: 12px/20px Tahoma; white-space: normal; orphans: 2; letter-spacing: 2px; color: rgb(102,102,102); word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-size-adjust: auto; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px\"><img border=\"0\" alt=\"\" width=\"500\" src=\"http://www.edifier.com/sce2009/product/speaker/e10/9.jpg\" /></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify; widows: 2; text-transform: none; text-indent: 0px; font: 12px/20px Tahoma; white-space: normal; orphans: 2; letter-spacing: 2px; color: rgb(102,102,102); word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-size-adjust: auto; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px\">漫步者e10的中高音箱体还特殊设计了一个与桌面约100度的小仰角，不仅贴合主机的自然角度，更与人体的聆听习惯一致，从而获得最佳的声场效果。</p>\r\n<p align=\"center\" style=\"widows: 2; text-transform: none; text-indent: 0px; font: 12px/20px Tahoma; white-space: normal; orphans: 2; letter-spacing: 2px; color: rgb(102,102,102); word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-size-adjust: auto; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px\"><img border=\"0\" alt=\"\" width=\"500\" src=\"http://www.edifier.com/sce2009/product/speaker/e10/10.jpg\" /></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify; widows: 2; text-transform: none; text-indent: 0px; font: 12px/20px Tahoma; white-space: normal; orphans: 2; letter-spacing: 2px; color: rgb(102,102,102); word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-size-adjust: auto; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px\">在优秀的单元配置之外，电路的反复打磨与声学性能的调校是释放好声音的核心因素。漫步者e10内置高品质DSP 音频处理器（电子分频），为中高音和低音扬声器提供理想的频率分配及动态范围控制。而且，漫步者e10还集成了两枚TAS5707高性能D级数字功率放大器，提供充足的功率输出和理想的频率分配，保证音质震撼澎湃。</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify; widows: 2; text-transform: none; text-indent: 0px; font: 12px/20px Tahoma; white-space: normal; orphans: 2; letter-spacing: 2px; color: rgb(102,102,102); word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-size-adjust: auto; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px\"><b>简洁连线操控设置，应用体验出色</b></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify; widows: 2; text-transform: none; text-indent: 0px; font: 12px/20px Tahoma; white-space: normal; orphans: 2; letter-spacing: 2px; color: rgb(102,102,102); word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-size-adjust: auto; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px\">漫步者e10在拥有简约造型的同时，还有着简洁的连线与操作设置，为您带来得心应手的操控体验。</p>\r\n<p align=\"center\" style=\"widows: 2; text-transform: none; text-indent: 0px; font: 12px/20px Tahoma; white-space: normal; orphans: 2; letter-spacing: 2px; color: rgb(102,102,102); word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-size-adjust: auto; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px\"><img border=\"0\" alt=\"\" width=\"500\" src=\"http://www.edifier.com/sce2009/product/speaker/e10/11.jpg\" /></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify; widows: 2; text-transform: none; text-indent: 0px; font: 12px/20px Tahoma; white-space: normal; orphans: 2; letter-spacing: 2px; color: rgb(102,102,102); word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-size-adjust: auto; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px\">由于一体化设计省去了外置低音炮，桌面变得更为简洁明快，而且音源只采用AUX输入，因此相对传统的多媒体音箱，e10的连线要简单得多，在主箱底部设置主副箱体连接、音源输入与电源输入，使用更便捷。</p>\r\n<p align=\"center\" style=\"widows: 2; text-transform: none; text-indent: 0px; font: 12px/20px Tahoma; white-space: normal; orphans: 2; letter-spacing: 2px; color: rgb(102,102,102); word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-size-adjust: auto; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px\"><img border=\"0\" alt=\"\" width=\"500\" src=\"http://www.edifier.com/sce2009/product/speaker/e10/12.jpg\" /></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify; widows: 2; text-transform: none; text-indent: 0px; font: 12px/20px Tahoma; white-space: normal; orphans: 2; letter-spacing: 2px; color: rgb(102,102,102); word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-size-adjust: auto; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px\">而在操控设置上，漫步者e10采用了键控操作系统，音量增减及开关机三颗按键装置在随手可触的主箱体上，操控直观，得心应手。</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify; widows: 2; text-transform: none; text-indent: 0px; font: 12px/20px Tahoma; white-space: normal; orphans: 2; letter-spacing: 2px; color: rgb(102,102,102); word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-size-adjust: auto; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px\"><b>完美融入多种环境，尽显个性品位</b></p>\r\n<p align=\"center\" style=\"widows: 2; text-transform: none; text-indent: 0px; font: 12px/20px Tahoma; white-space: normal; orphans: 2; letter-spacing: 2px; color: rgb(102,102,102); word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-size-adjust: auto; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px\"><img border=\"0\" alt=\"\" width=\"500\" src=\"http://www.edifier.com/sce2009/product/speaker/e10/13.jpg\" /></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify; widows: 2; text-transform: none; text-indent: 0px; font: 12px/20px Tahoma; white-space: normal; orphans: 2; letter-spacing: 2px; color: rgb(102,102,102); word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-size-adjust: auto; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px\">虽然在音源设置方面较为单一，但漫步者e10同样拥有出色的造型设计与优秀的音质表现，而且操控设置也别具一格，足够胜任日常桌面应用，比如与台式机、笔记本电脑等搭配伴音使用，充分满足用户影音娱乐需求。</p>\r\n<p align=\"center\" style=\"widows: 2; text-transform: none; text-indent: 0px; font: 12px/20px Tahoma; white-space: normal; orphans: 2; letter-spacing: 2px; color: rgb(102,102,102); word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-size-adjust: auto; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px\"><img border=\"0\" alt=\"\" width=\"500\" src=\"http://www.edifier.com/sce2009/product/speaker/e10/14.jpg\" /></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify; widows: 2; text-transform: none; text-indent: 0px; font: 12px/20px Tahoma; white-space: normal; orphans: 2; letter-spacing: 2px; color: rgb(102,102,102); word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-size-adjust: auto; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px\">不过，漫步者e10有着可爱的&ldquo;蜗牛&rdquo;造型，在好音效的基础上，还能为用户提供全新的视觉感受。这种颠覆传统的造型设计，还能走出电脑桌，在家居环境找到一席之地，并可与家具装饰完美融合，为你的音乐生活注入更多个性色彩。</p>\r\n<p align=\"center\" style=\"widows: 2; text-transform: none; text-indent: 0px; font: 12px/20px Tahoma; white-space: normal; orphans: 2; letter-spacing: 2px; color: rgb(102,102,102); word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-size-adjust: auto; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px\"><img border=\"0\" alt=\"\" width=\"500\" src=\"http://www.edifier.com/sce2009/product/speaker/e10/15.jpg\" /></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify; widows: 2; text-transform: none; text-indent: 0px; font: 12px/20px Tahoma; white-space: normal; orphans: 2; letter-spacing: 2px; color: rgb(102,102,102); word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-size-adjust: auto; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px\">作为e系列2.2阵营的入门级音响，e10除了具备一贯的优秀造型之外，其音质表现同样出色，总计30W的额定输出功率，已经达到中高级桌面级音响的水平，其强悍的低音效果与均衡的中高音表现，让人不能相信体积小巧的它竟然还蕴藏着如此动听的声音。作为漫步者时尚e系列的最新作品，e10相对亲民的价格，必将掀起一阵时尚旋风。</p>','images/201304/thumb_img/1605_thumb_G_1367196687473.jpg','images/201304/goods_img/1605_G_1367196687527.jpg','images/201304/source_img/1605_G_1367196687382.jpg','1','','1','1','0','0','1367196687','100','0','0','0','0','0','0','1398985387','68','','0','0','0','0');
